topic.title: Nutritional Status Observation - conformance rules

section.p: This template describes the overall nutritional status of the patient including findings related to nutritional status.

ol.li:
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] templateId ( CONF:1098-29843, CONF:1098-29844 ) such that it
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @root="2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.4.124"
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="OBS" Observation (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.5.6 HL7ActClass) (CONF:1098-29841)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @moodCode="EVN" Event (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.5.1001 HL7ActMood) (CONF:1098-29842)
SHALL contain at least one [1..*] id (CONF:1098-29845)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] code (CONF:1098-29846)/@code="75305-3" Nutrition status (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.6.1 LOINC) (CONF:1098-29897, CONF:1098-29898)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] statusCode (CONF:1098-29852)/@code="completed" Completed (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.5.14 ActStatus) (CONF:1098-29853)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] value with @xsi:type="CD", which SHOULD be selected from ValueSet Nutritional Status 2.16.840.1.113883.1.11.20.2.7 DYNAMIC (CONF:1098-29854)
